          <h3 data-en="Pass a State Surveillance Oversight Law" data-es="Aprobar una Ley Estatal de Supervisión de Vigilancia">Pass a State Surveillance Oversight Law</h3>
          <p class="petition-card__sms" data-en='Text "sign PPGCFY" to 50409' data-es='Escribe "sign PPGCFY" al 50409'>Text "sign PPGCFY" to 50409</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://resist.bot/petitions/PMPSFP" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="petition-card">
          <h3 data-en="Ban Dark Money in Colorado Elections" data-es="Prohibir el Dinero Oscuro en Elecciones de Colorado">Ban Dark Money in Colorado Elections</h3>
          <p class="petition-card__sms" data-en='Text "sign PMPSFP" to 50409' data-es='Escribe "sign PMPSFP" al 50409'>Text "sign PMPSFP" to 50409</p>
        </a>
